37#ifndef _NVPAIR_IMPL_H_
38#define _NVPAIR_IMPL_H_
39
40#ifdef __FreeBSD__
41#include <sys/nv.h>
42#else
43#include "nv.h"
44#endif
45#include <sys/queue.h>
46
47#if !defined(_KERNEL) && !defined(_STANDALONE)
48#include <stdint.h>
49#endif
50
51TAILQ_HEAD(nvl_head, nvpair);
52
53void nvpair_assert(const nvpair_t *nvp);
54nvlist_t *nvpair_nvlist(const nvpair_t *nvp);
55nvpair_t *nvpair_next(const nvpair_t *nvp);
56nvpair_t *nvpair_prev(const nvpair_t *nvp);
57void nvpair_insert(struct nvl_head *head, nvpair_t *nvp, nvlist_t *nvl);
58void nvpair_remove(struct nvl_head *head, nvpair_t *nvp, const nvlist_t *nvl);
59size_t nvpair_header_size(void);
60size_t nvpair_size(const nvpair_t *nvp);
61const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack(bool isbe, const unsigned char *ptr,
62 size_t *leftp, nvpair_t **nvpp);
63void nvpair_free_structure(nvpair_t *nvp);
64void nvpair_init_datasize(nvpair_t *nvp);
65const char *nvpair_type_string(int type);
66
67/* Pack functions. */
68unsigned char *nvpair_pack_header(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
69 size_t *leftp);
70unsigned char *nvpair_pack_null(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
71 size_t *leftp);
72unsigned char *nvpair_pack_bool(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
73 size_t *leftp);
74unsigned char *nvpair_pack_number(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
75 size_t *leftp);
76unsigned char *nvpair_pack_string(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
77 size_t *leftp);
78unsigned char *nvpair_pack_descriptor(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
79 int64_t *fdidxp, size_t *leftp);
80unsigned char *nvpair_pack_binary(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
81 size_t *leftp);
82unsigned char *nvpair_pack_nvlist_up(unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
83unsigned char *nvpair_pack_bool_array(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
84 size_t *leftp);
85unsigned char *nvpair_pack_number_array(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
86 size_t *leftp);
87unsigned char *nvpair_pack_string_array(const nvpair_t *nvp, unsigned char *ptr,
88 size_t *leftp);
89unsigned char *nvpair_pack_descriptor_array(const nvpair_t *nvp,
90 unsigned char *ptr, int64_t *fdidxp, size_t *leftp);
91unsigned char *nvpair_pack_nvlist_array_next(unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
92
93/* Unpack data functions. */
94const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_header(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
95 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
96const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_null(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
97 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
98const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_bool(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
99 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
100const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_number(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
101 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
102const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_string(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
103 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
104const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_nvlist(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
105 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp, size_t nfds, nvlist_t **child);
106const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_descriptor(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
107 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp, const int *fds, size_t nfds);
108const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_binary(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
109 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
110const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_bool_array(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
111 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
112const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_number_array(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
113 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
114const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_string_array(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
115 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp);
116const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_descriptor_array(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
117 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp, const int *fds, size_t nfds);
118const unsigned char *nvpair_unpack_nvlist_array(bool isbe, nvpair_t *nvp,
119 const unsigned char *ptr, size_t *leftp, nvlist_t **firstel);

121#endif /* !_NVPAIR_IMPL_H_ */
